    <h3 align=center id=qname>Tunic of Riddosan</h3><hr size=1>
	 <table width=100% cellpadding=3 cellspacing=0 border=0>
	 <tr><td valign=top>
	 <table cellpadding=1 cellspacing=1 border=0 align=left>
	 <tr><td><b>Starts in:</b></td><td><a href='http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Odus/Paineel.htm'>Paineel</a></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Who:</b></td><td><a href=http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=5439></a></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Rating:</b></td><td>Average (3.00)</td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Estimated Time:</b></td><td>days</td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Minimum Level:</b></td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td><b>Best Class:</b></td><td>Shad</td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Additional Zones:</b></span><li><a href=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/Feerrott.htm>Feerrott</a></li><li><a href=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/Freeport.htm>Freeport West</a></li><li><a href=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/Najena.htm>Najena</a></li><li><a href=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/QeynosA.htm>Qeynos Aqueducts</a></li><li><a href=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/Runnyeye.htm>Runnyeye</a></li><li><a href=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Odus/The_Warrens.html>Warrens</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Related Creatures:</b></span><li><a href=http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=2676>Lyris Moonbane</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><span id=rt><b>Related Quests:</b></span><li><a href=quest.html?quest=1239>Cold Iron</a></li></ul></td></tr></td></tr></table>This is a followup to the Cold Iron Quest.  Say "what more important task?" to Royal Guard Sheltuin and he will ask a favor for a knight.  Respond "I will be the knight" and  he then gives you a chest to deliver to Lyris Moonbane the necro guildmaster in the Qeynos aqueducts.<br><br>When you give her the chest you gain faction and exp and she gives you a glass jar with 4 slots and asks if you're ready for your first assisgnment. Respond with "what assignment? and she tells you she needs 4 substances for something she's workin on:<br><br>- 2 portions of a goblin substance (which drops in runnyeye off the janitor)<br>- one portion of a green river sludge (found in river near oggok in feerott at approx loc 137, 704 get someone to cast enduring breath) <br>- and one portion of an experimental nature (given by driana poxborne after you give her 3 regent pouches which drop off najena mages.  She is located in west freeport sewers)<br><br>After gettin all 4 hit combine and return the jar to lyris moonbane she then adds a gem to the jar making it what she calls the harbringer of bertoxxulous and tells you to deliver the substance.  Respond "where do i deliver the substance?"  and she tells you to take it to the river source in the warrens dungeon and it will poison the kobolds water supply..<br><br>when you give it to the river source you get back an empty jar.  Take the empty jar back to the Royal Sheltuin in Paineel and you recieve the tunic of riddosan!  </td></tr>
	 <tr><td id=rt valign=top>Reward(s):</td></tr>
	 <tr><td valign=top><li><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=6451">Tunic of Riddosan</a></li></td></tr>
