dman of cazic thule can be the army of lesser beings who believed the lord they shared favored them more than it". <br>So i think the grimy lance is the good weapon : the ghost may unsealed its power. <br><br><br>Imothep Knight of Fear of the 27 circle. <br>Ayonae Ro <br>"Fear is our Armor" <br><br>So i think we are in a good way to discover a lovely mini epic weapon for mid level sk. <br>So if there is some high levels sk that travel in Stone brunt mountain, could you please try give the spirit the lance ? <br>Thank you in advance. <br><br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Imothep Knight of Fear of the 27 Circle.<br>Ayonae Ro</td></tr>
